- What was not tested: I did not test a real paid third-party provider. The proof covers the product `models.json` generation path, legacy catalog-only cleanup path, auth-profile migration path, fail-closed persistence behavior, and pi model discovery compatibility with temporary local agent dirs and redacted dummy keys.

